high_descs: Walk over to the sink on your right.
Pick up the potato out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk towards the door, turn right again to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the potato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave up and remove the heated potato, then close the microwave.
Look down at the kitchen sink in front of you.
Put the heated potato in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Cook the potato in the microwave and pick it back up.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the microwave directly on your right.
Heat the potato in the microwave, then take it out and close the microwave.
Put the potato on the left side of the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot potato in a sink.
